<A>__{nick turns away, resumes his drink. nick's pov in the mirror behind the bar: two new japanese men step in the door. early twenties, spiky hair, dark versace suits.}
<B>__{number one}
<A>__{wears tortoise shell shades. he coolly checks out the room then nods to }
<B>__{number two}
<A>__{who pulls a spas 12, automatic shotgun from under his coat, and spits out three rounds. a window shatters. everyone hits the floor.}
<B>__{number one}
<A>__{slowly walks toward cavello's table.}
<B>__{number two}
<A>__{covers the floor. abolofia's bodyguards show their empty hands.}
<B>__{nick and charlie}
<A>__{on the floor. they don't have the artillery for this guy either.}
<B>__{at the table}
<A>__{our japanese businessman knows these people. he eyes them contemptuously. abolofia has put enough people in this situation to be philosophical about it. he stops chewing. a tiny hand motion to his bodyguards is enough to stop any precipitous action.}
<C>__{number one}
<P>__{(in japanese)}
<D>__{give it to me.}
